"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/scrx92.jpg"}], "slug": "castaway-station", "storyline": "\"Our ambition was\u2026quantum. We truly believed we were prepared to explore the deep universe. The hubris.\"\u2028\u2028\n\nWelcome to Castaway Station, an exciting survival game that takes you on an unintended journey on a hostile planet after a catastrophic accident on your space cruiser. The U.N. Kobayashi breaks up over Prima Centauri B and the survivors barely escape to the planet's surface. Chief engineer Yu Kato is able to land a shuttle and establishes Castaway Station. She begins her journey to explore the planet, find other survivors and bring them together. They must use all their wits and skills, along with any tools they scavenge, to survive as they face undiscovered local lifeforms. They won't ever get home.\u2028\u2028", "summary": "An anomaly has destroyed your cruiser, stranding you alone on a hostile planet. Castaway Station is a roguelike deck-builder game with limited-use cards and permanent death. Complete dangerous missions to locate other survivors and gather the resources you need to live another day.", "themes": [{"id": 1, "name": "Action"}, {"id": 21, "name": "Survival"}], "url": "https://www.igdb.com/games/castaway-station", "videos": [{"id": 111543, "name": "Launch Trailer", "video_id": "n3faKfHeiJw", "url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=n3faKfHeiJw", "title": "Castaway Station Official Trailer", "thumb": "https://i.ytimg.com/vi/n3faKfHeiJw/hqdefault.jpg"}]}